In debian

* cd ${HOME}
* vim .config/openbox/lxde-rc.xml
* find label <keyboard> then insert your settings
  e.g.

'''
<keybind key="C-A-t">
 <action name="Execute">
  <command>lxterminal</command>
 </action>
</keybind>
<keybind key="C-A-f">
 <action name="Execute">
  <command>pcmanfm</command>
 </action>
</keybind>
'''

* restart lxde and see if it works
